data.description: New and Improved Price! ***** NO HOA!! **** NO CDD!! **** Video Tour: https://youtu.be/uIuxaa8QPA8   Discover true pride of ownership in this exceptional home, where cherished memories await! Spend your days basking in the sun-drenched screen-enclosed pool or host late-night cookouts on the recently paved spacious lanai, an extended 30 x 20 living space in itself. With a split floor plan, parents and guests enjoy added privacy, making sleepovers a breeze. Relax on your hammock under the shade of mature trees, surrounded by a lush lawn and impeccable landscaping. You'll relish the gentle breezes in this sought-after Kissimmee location. Best of all, there's NO HOA and NO CDD to worry about! Congratulations on your newly remodeled home! With its fresh coat of interior paint and fully remodeled kitchen, your home is sure to impress any visitor. The granite countertops and upgraded LG stainless steel appliances in your kitchen are both functional and stylish, making meal prep and hosting a breeze. Additionally, the wood look tile flooring throughout the living areas and master bedroom provide easy maintenance and a cohesive design element throughout your home. With no carpets to worry about, your home truly is turnkey and ready for you to enjoy! Featuring Nest Thermostat. A modern marvel in home climate control. With its sleek design and smart technology, it brings unmatched convenience and energy savings to your household. Enjoy personalized temperature settings, remote access, and savings on your energy bills. Situated on a corner lot in a quiet cul-de-sac, you'll experience minimal traffic. Enjoy a short 12-minute drive to the airport and just 10 minutes to the new 417/Turnpike exit, conveniently close to Medical City. This gem is being sold 'As Is,' so don't miss this is A Must See!   For all specific details, room measurements, and restrictions, we encourage buyers and their agents to verify. Pre-approval or proof of funds required. FAR/BAR-AS-IS Only completed offers will be presented. Call or text Listing Agent for any questions. Call today to schedule a viewing and take the next step toward making this house your home!!
